description:
Kaley Cuoco [The Big Bang Theory, The Flight Attendant] joins Anna to talk about horses, sex, not being funny, her love of television, the disappointment of birthdays, auditioning, meeting her husband, her new show The Flight Attendant (on HBO MAX) and more. Later in the episode Anna welcomes back clinical sexologist, author and sex coach Dr. Pattie Britton who shares her thoughts on porn, masturbation and threesomes.

For more from Dr. Pattie visit her websites www.drpattibritton.com and www.sexcoachu.com

Maker's Mark So ladies, remember to pour yourself into everything you do, and to reach for a bourbon that’s made with a personal (feminine) touch. In fact, go ahead and pour yourself some Maker’s Mark right now and raise a glass to you and all of the remarkable women in your life. And remember - Maker’s Mark crafts their bourbon carefully, and they ask that you enjoy it that way.

Peacock Saved by the Bell is available now on PEACOCK – the streaming service from NBCUniversal. Sign up at PeacockTV.com to stream now.
